{"article_id":"EdiYzgxRFG6uX40G","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"LISTEN TO ARTICLE 2:43","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"SHARE THIS ARTICLE","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"Share Tweet","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"Post Email","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"President Donald Trump was briefed Thursday night about the monthly employment report","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"issued Friday morning in Washington","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"and signaled in advance","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"that the numbers were going to be favorable ,","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"breaking with past practice of presidents","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"who avoided disclosure of market-sensitive information .","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"\" Looking forward to seeing the employment numbers at 8:30 this morning , \"","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"the president tweeted at 7:21 a.m. in Washington .","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"Looking forward to seeing the employment numbers at 8:30 this morning .","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"June 1 , 2018","depth":5},{"id":16,"text":"The Department of Labor reported at 8:30 a.m.","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"that unemployment in the U.S. had dropped to its lowest level since 1969","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"as the economy added a higher-than-expected 223,000 jobs in May .","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"Larry Kudlow , director of Trump ' s National Economic Council , said in a brief interview","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"that Trump had the numbers last night","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"and his tweet wasn ' t meant to signal a positive report .","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"\" I don ' t think","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"he gave anything away \" in the tweet ,","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"Kudlow said in a separate interview with CNBC .","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"The breach of precedent is just the latest in a string of instances","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"in which Trump has broken with normal presidential practice .","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"Just this week , he pardoned Dinesh D ' Souza , a conservative commentator","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"convicted of breaking campaign finance law .","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"Presidents usually hold off on controversial clemency decisions","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"until their terms are nearly over .","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"Trump ' s social-media post was met with tepid reaction in financial markets ,","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"where investors assess more than just the headline numbers .","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"U.S. stocks jumped in early trading .","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"After Trump ' s tweet , the two-year Treasury yield climbed one basis point ,","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"while the dollar stayed flat .","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"Trump 's Tweet","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"The dollar 's move pre-jobs report was huge in comparison to how it typically trades pre-release","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"Source :","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"Some White House officials get access to the monthly employment data the day","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"before the report is released publicly ,","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"and the president is routinely briefed on the numbers on Thursday .","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"Most jobs reports are released on the first Friday of each month .","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"There are government procedures for officials","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"who handle undisclosed numbers","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"that require a delay","depth":14},{"id":46,"text":"of commenting","depth":14},{"id":47,"text":"until one hour","depth":13},{"id":48,"text":"after they ' re released .","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"\" They ' re treated like state secrets , \"","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"Alan Krueger , former chairman of the Council of Economic Advisers in the Obama administration , said in an interview with Radio","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"before the employment report came out .","depth":12},{"id":52,"text":"The jobs report also showed","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"wage gains","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"-- mediocre for years --","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"exceeded estimates ,","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"rising 2.7 percent from a year earlier .","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"\" It doesn ' t look good , \"","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"said Mark Hamrick , Bankrate.com ' s senior economic analyst .","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"\" As has been said so many times by the president ' s supporters as well as his critics ,","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"this is another case","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"where it would be better for President Trump would be wise to spend his time","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"doing something other than tweeting . \"","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"Omair Sharif , a senior U.S. economist at Societe Generale , said","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"the tweet creates a conundrum for traders ahead of future jobs reports .","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"\" I don ' t know","depth":14},{"id":66,"text":"if people should object ,","depth":14},{"id":67,"text":"but it adds a little extra uncertainty prior to the release","depth":14},{"id":68,"text":"that could impact what people in the market are thinking","depth":15},{"id":69,"text":"just before the data come out , \"","depth":15},{"id":70,"text":"he said .","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"\" If don ' t get a tweet next time ,","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"people will think","depth":13},{"id":73,"text":"it ' s going to be a bad print . \"","depth":13}],"relations":[{"parent":147,"left":0,"right":146,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":146,"left":76,"right":145,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":76,"left":1,"right":75,"relation":"restatement","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":75,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":145,"left":87,"right":144,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":87,"left":81,"right":86,